				\begin{document}$\upmu$\end{document}m size resulting in a 0.15 × 0.15 arcsec2 field of view (FOV) per pixel. The mosaic has a physical size of 482 × 212 mm, and covers a FOV of 1.04°×0.44° or 0.46 square degrees. The HgCdTe Hawaii 2RG arrays are standard devices sensitive in the 0.8 to 1.7 \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
